"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":3.601,"vote_average":0},{"width":2048,"height":1151,"file_path":"/wPhZM3T16j92jLoGEmDvaqG2Dc8.png","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.779,"vote_average":0}],"posters":[{"width":890,"height":1336,"file_path":"/dEk0kC7uq54g7cVheQBgiAcCuNH.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":0.666,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1587,"height":2245,"file_path":"/f1fodFJqkOq22nHta90ClDzV1gG.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":0.707,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":2000,"height":2941,"file_path":"/rL43aerd6hBYUvgBj0dE1kYMcgt.jpg","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":0.68,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":935,"height":1247,"file_path":"/AuVdCfAPDeAG0Dy36GH6OdAvPHZ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.75,"vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":1440,"height":810,"file_path":"/4DDKUnw63RXdz9MOm3bTkbaMwV5.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1899,"height":1068,"file_path":"/rba72d1kQjI1PEOpelsT1Z5lX5H.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1440,"height":810,"file_path":"/wIKP4aGhLQjg1cnDmReHcDft58q.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1440,"height":810,"file_path":"/6CxXMC0Z6Q5iyk7w6N8KIKa7YV4.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1440,"height":810,"file_path":"/w26hXhAssh6sKmgO56PnBdKgBBF.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/7hRESdigqUSniO11Y0MsX7ztDD.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/JxisDW97mbtB0LXK7YMIUuhz46.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/2XCiSBqrBFJi67tyvP07miXMCpK.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/ci3cJRZMWRdp4QrjaVoBOu2rpVB.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/qu9Xrt1y8KInF2nfAUtbr1fc6oM.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/xXsv6dK4hs1OAqJHkImZwM6RB3J.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/sQhKxo30JLjfsOrdQC5dR8ee8O4.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:43:31.013+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":103,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ketika Ambar & Dika pindah setelah kematian orang tua mereka, tidak pernah terpikirkan apa yang seharusnya menjadi awal baru berubah menjadi awal kesengsaraan terbesar dalam hidup mereka. Semua akibat kemampuan Ambar merasakan yang tak terlihat, yang didapatkan setelah mengalami gangguan penglihatan. Berbeda dengan sambutan didapat di Panti Jompo Masa Toea, Ambar mendapatkan bayangan masa lalu yang menakutkan. Dia menemukan bahwa telah terjadi pembantaian di rumah yang sama bertahun-tahun yang lalu. Sebuah entitas wanita Belanda, Ivanna, muncul dalam visi Ambar, memberinya sekilas tragedi di mana dia dipenggal oleh imperialis keji. Pada hari Idul Fitri, Nenek Ani ditemukan tewas dalam genangan darah, dipenggal. Ambar menduga tragedi itu mungkin terkait dengan penemuan peti yang berisi pernak-pernik dan patung tanpa kepala di ruang bawah tanah paviliun panti jompo. Sekarang, Ambar harus menyelesaikan dendam makhluk yang perlahan merayap ke dalam hidup mereka, bahkan untuk kepala mereka."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":103,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://mdentertainment.com/pictures/uncategorized/ivanna/","overview":"Ambar & Dika have just begun with a new chapter of life when years-old grudge of a malicious entity unfolds before their eyes. With a gift she unwillingly has, Ambar is now forced to finish the vengeance of the entity, a headless Dutch spirit, Ivanna."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":103,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ambar et Dika viennent de commencer un nouveau chapitre de leur vie lorsque la rancune d'une entité malveillante vieille de plusieurs années se déroule sous leurs yeux. Avec un cadeau qu'elle a involontairement, Ambar est maintenant obligée de terminer la vengeance de l'entité, un esprit hollandais sans tête, Ivanna..."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ambar y su familia estaban aterrorizados cuando celebraban Lebaran en el área de Bandung. Ambar, una hermosa joven que tiene una visión limitada, puede ver cosas que otras personas no pueden ver."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Amber နဲ့ Dika တို့မောင်နှမကမိဘတွေဆုံးသွားတဲ့နောက်မှာ သူ့မိဘတွေရဲ့မိတ်ဆွေ အဒေါ် Wati တို့နဲ့ ဂေဟာမှာ လာနေကြပါတယ်။Amber က မျက်လုံးခွဲစိတ်ပြီးနောက်ပိုင်းမှာ တခြားသူတွေမမြင်နိုင်တဲ့အရာတွေကို မြင်နိုင်စွမ်းရှိနေတဲ့သူပါ။သူတို့သွားနေတဲ့ ဂေဟာကတော့ ဟိုးအရင် အင်ဒိုနီးရှားနိုင်ငံကိုအင်္ဂလိပ်တွေ အုပ်စိုးတဲ့အချိန်တုန်းက ဒတ်ချ်လူမျိုးမိသားစု နေခဲ့တဲ့နေရာပါ။အင်ဒိုနီးရှားနိုင်ငံကို ဂျပန်တွေ လာသိမ်းတဲ့အချိန်မှာတော့အဲဒီအိမ်မှာပဲ ဒတ်ချ်အမျိုးသမီးတစ်ယောက် ရက်ရက်စက်စက်ခေါင်းဖြတ်ပြီး အသတ်ခံထားရပါတယ်။သူတို့ရောက်သွားတဲ့အချိန်မှာမှ အဲဒီအမျိုးသမီးရဲ့ဝိညာဉ်က အကြောင်းတိုက်ဆိုင်ပြီး ပေါ်လာတဲ့အချိန်မှာဘာတွေဆက်ဖြစ်လာမလဲဆိုတာ ဇာတ်လမ်းထဲမှာပဲ ကြည့်ရှုလိုက်ပါ။"},"name":"","iso_639_1":"my","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Burmese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ambar y Dika acaban de comenzar con un nuevo capítulo de la vida cuando el rencor de años de una entidad maliciosa se desarrolla ante sus ojos. Con un regalo que tiene de mala gana, Ambar ahora se ve obligada a terminar la venganza de la entidad, un espíritu holandés sin cabeza, Ivanna."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Иванна","runtime":103,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Потеряв родителей, практически слепая девушка-подросток Амбар вместе с младшим братом приезжает жить к друзьям в дом престарелых. Накануне окончания Рамадана почти все постояльцы разъехались праздновать со своими семьями, и брат с сестрой оказываются в небольшой тёплой компании. Доставая залетевший в сарай фрисби, ребята обнаруживают там подвал, а в подвале — странную безголовую скульптуру. Этой же ночью Амбар слышит и видит призраков далёкого прошлого, а на утро скульптура из подвала оказывается в общей гостиной."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"伊万娜","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ambar 和他的家人在万隆地区庆祝黎巴嫩节时受到了惊吓。Ambar，一位视力有限的美丽年轻女子，能够看到其他人看不到的东西。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"伊萬娜","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ambar 和他的家人在萬隆地區慶祝黎巴嫩節時受到了驚嚇。 Ambar，一位視力有限的美麗年輕女子，能夠看到其他人看不到的東西。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ambar a Dika právě začínají novou životní kapitolu, když se jim před očima rozvine léta stará zášť zákeřné entity. Díky daru, který nechtěně má, je nyní Ambar nucena dokončit pomstu oné entity, bezhlavého holandského ducha Ivanny."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"이반나","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"암바와 디카는 이제 막 새로운 인생의 장을 시작하려던 찰나, 악의적인 존재의 오랜 원한을 마주하고. 원치 않는 능력을 얻은 암바르는 이제 머리 없는 네덜란드 정령 이반나의 복수를 끝내야만 합니다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"อิวานนา ผีทวงหัว","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"อัมบาร์และดิกาเพิ่งเริ่มต้นชีวิตบทใหม่ แต่แล้วได้มีสิ่งชั่วร้ายที่ก่อตัวขึ้นต่อหน้าต่อตาพวกเขา ด้วยของขวัญที่เธอได้รับอย่างไม่เต็มใจ ตอนนี้อัมบาร์ถูกบังคับให้ต้องเผชิญกับความแค้นของอิวานนา วิญญาณสาวดัตช์หัวขาด"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":509585,"adult":false,"title":"7500","video":false,"overview":"When terrorists try to seize control of a Berlin-Paris flight, a soft-spoken young American co-pilot struggles to save the lives of the passengers and crew while forging a surprising connection with one of the hijackers.","genre_ids":[53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8453,"vote_count":908,"poster_path":"/hL2uecLh2rTTbuVbOriXP0PhqIJ.jpg","release_date":"2019-12-26","vote_average":6.146,"backdrop_path":"/72QAA1dKmOrqZafe7UhHafDTjEq.jpg","original_title":"7500","original_language":"en"},{"id":623464,"adult":false,"title":"Zombie Tidal Wave","video":false,"overview":"A fisherman contends with an ocean-borne outbreak that threatens his seaside island community.","genre_ids":[28,12,878,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4592,"vote_count":62,"poster_path":"/bdlWPVFMsBchv07HxF2khcdCEwZ.jpg","release_date":"2019-08-17","vote_average":4.435,"backdrop_path":"/3PlHbkANRZRcIYPi5sPLvb4oGAM.jpg","original_title":"Zombie Tidal Wave","original_language":"en"},{"id":1188456,"adult":false,"title":"A Strange House","video":false,"overview":"Amemiya is an unpopular Youtuber who specializes in the occult. One day, his manager brings him a floor plan with an inscrutable point. With the help of Kurihara and Yuzuki, he begins to look into the plan and reveal the mystery behind.","genre_ids":[53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7655,"vote_count":21,"poster_path":"/uYWD7TmbLLPGODczH9NGVDqE8dY.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-15","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/5UOOA9RUazq4S3D9t4ljCVjlpYd.jpg","original_title":"変な家","original_language":"ja"},{"id":4538,"adult":false,"title":"The Darjeeling Limited","video":false,"overview":"Three American brothers who have not spoken to each other in a year set off on a train voyage across India with a plan to find themselves and bond with each other -- to become brothers again like they used to be. Their \"spiritual quest\", however, veers rapidly off-course (due to events involving over-the-counter pain killers, Indian cough syrup, and pepper spray).","genre_ids":[12,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.6017,"vote_count":3855,"poster_path":"/oSW5OVXTulaIXcoNwJAp5YEKpbP.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-07","vote_average":7.152,"backdrop_path":"/hKJ513GbmTSmTXJU1uCXclh5Wkh.jpg","original_title":"The Darjeeling Limited","original_language":"en"},{"id":420634,"adult":false,"title":"Terrifier","video":false,"overview":"A maniacal clown named Art terrorizes three young women on Halloween night and everyone else who stands in his way.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.9957,"vote_count":2883,"poster_path":"/fjXqhGmaeQpB73WerhrYU6HlyV5.jpg","release_date":"2018-01-25","vote_average":6.324,"backdrop_path":"/naNXYdBzTEb1KwOdi1RbBkM9Zv1.jpg","original_title":"Terrifier","original_language":"en"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.3785,"vote_count":27338,"poster_path":"/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-01","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg","original_title":"Joker","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":23.0611,"vote_count":11386,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":791373,"adult":false,"title":"Zack Snyder's Justice League","video":false,"overview":"Determined to ensure Superman's ultimate sacrifice was not in vain, Bruce Wayne aligns forces with Diana Prince with plans to recruit a team of metahumans to protect the world from an approaching threat of catastrophic proportions.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.0834,"vote_count":10641,"poster_path":"/tnAuB8q5vv7Ax9UAEje5Xi4BXik.jpg","release_date":"2021-03-18","vote_average":8.096,"backdrop_path":"/13Nz8EchKRdCgJcKdEoJAnpiVn2.jpg","original_title":"Zack Snyder's Justice League","original_language":"en"},{"id":466272,"adult":false,"title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","video":false,"overview":"Los Angeles, 1969. TV star Rick Dalton, a struggling actor specializing in westerns, and stuntman Cliff Booth, his best friend, try to survive in a constantly changing movie industry. Dalton is the neighbor of the young and promising actress and model Sharon Tate, who has just married the prestigious Polish director Roman Polanski…","genre_ids":[35,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.2711,"vote_count":14577,"poster_path":"/8j58iEBw9pOXFD2L