, a 17-year-old Elio spends his days in his family's villa in Italy. One day Oliver, a graduate student, arrives to assist Elio's father, a professor of Greco-Roman culture. Soon, Elio and Oliver discover a summer that will alter their lives forever.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.9765,"vote_count":12603,"poster_path":"/mZ4gBdfkhP9tvLH1DO4m4HYtiyi.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-01","vote_average":8.096,"backdrop_path":"/fwf4L3r2ZU9ptOB9nOo5nuVLo1i.jpg","original_title":"Call Me by Your Name","original_language":"en"},{"id":324857,"adult":false,"title":"Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse","video":false,"overview":"Struggling to find his place in the world while juggling school and family, Brooklyn teenager Miles Morales is unexpectedly bitten by a radioactive spider and develops unfathomable powers just like the one and only Spider-Man. While wrestling with the implications of his new abilities, Miles discovers a super collider created by the madman Wilson \"Kingpin\" Fisk, causing others from across the Spider-Verse to be inadvertently transported to his dimension.","genre_ids":[16,28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":17.4153,"vote_count":16899,"poster_path":"/iiZZdoQBEYBv6id8su7ImL0oCbD.jpg","release_date":"2018-12-06","vote_average":8.393,"backdrop_path":"/8mnXR9rey5uQ08rZAvzojKWbDQS.jpg","original_title":"Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse","original_language":"en"},{"id":545609,"adult":false,"title":"Extraction","video":false,"overview":"A hardened gun-for-hire's latest mission becomes a soul-searching race to survive when he's sent into Bangladesh to rescue a drug lord's kidnapped son.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.5231,"vote_count":6491,"poster_path":"/nygOUcBKPHFTbxsYRFZVePqgPK6.jpg","release_date":"2020-04-23","vote_average":7.297,"backdrop_path":"/1R6cvRtZgsYCkh8UFuWFN33xBP4.jpg","original_title":"Extraction","original_language":"en"},{"id":490132,"adult":false,"title":"Green Book","video":false,"o